summary: This document is a Termination Agreement between Deutsche Bank AG and Southern Trust Company, Inc., effective December 7, 2016. It outlines the termination of a Global Master Repurchase Agreement, stating that there are no outstanding transactions or obligations between the parties as of the termination date.

persons.name: Mary Breslin
persons.context: Mary Breslin is identified as a Vice President at Deutsche Bank AG and is involved in the execution of the Termination Agreement.

keyFacts: The Termination Agreement is dated December 7, 2016.
The agreement terminates the Global Master Repurchase Agreement between Deutsche Bank AG and Southern Trust Company, Inc.
It states that there are no outstanding transactions or obligations between the parties.
The agreement allows for execution via electronic mail or facsimile.
Mary Breslin is mentioned as a signatory from Deutsche Bank AG.
